OL,3,GBLOOPERSCFault leaves over a minute of
OL,4,Cdead air on BBC One and BBC News
OL,5,Cchannel
OL,6,
OL,7,FA playout fault left over a minute of
OL,8,Fdead air on BBC One and the BBC News
OL,9,Fchannel this morning.
OL,11,FBBC One had been simulcasting the BBC
OL,12,FNews channel for some time when screens
OL,13,Fsuddenly went blank at 2am.
OL,15,FThe fault originated in playout for the
OL,16,FBBC News channel and affected both the
OL,17,FUK and international versions of the
OL,18,Fchannel.
OL,20,FAfter just over a minute of black and
OL,21,Fsilence, one of the news channel's
OL,22,Ffiller sequences appeared.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
