OL,3,GBLOOPERSCFault leaves over a minute of
OL,4,Cdead air on BBC One and BBC News
OL,5,Cchannel
OL,6,
OL,7,FAlmost a minute-a-half later, we
OL,8,Fcrashed into the scheduled live news
OL,9,Fprogramme, broadcast from Washington
OL,10,FDC, two-and-a-half minutes late.
